I"“<p>The cold and calculating Steward of Redwater. Anders hired the party to find and eliminate those responsible for attacks on trade caravans along the East Road towards Balnying. Upon their return, he insists that the mercenaries lie about the cause of the attacks, blaming everything on Disparia. When the party hesitated, he had them imprisoned. <br /><br /> The party learned of his involvement in a plot to assassinate the Duke Geoffrey and place blame on Disparians. They found him dead in the very same cell in which he had imprisoned them. A strange satyr-like creature was standing over him, dressed in green and wiping the blood from his hands.</p>
